      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f80ff-102">夏时制是一段时间内的年份时钟高级时间，通常通过 1 小时，若要利用扩展的夏时制的小时数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f80ff-102">Daylight saving time is a period during the year when the clock is advanced, usually by an hour, to take advantage of extended daylight hours.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f80ff-103">在该期间结束时，时钟重新设置为标准时间。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f80ff-103">At the end of the period, the clock is set back to the standard time.</span></span>  
  
> [!WARNING]
>  <span data-ttu-id="f80ff-104"><xref:System.Globalization.DaylightTime>返回对象<xref:System.TimeZone.GetDaylightChanges%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法只会识别时区调整规则的当前正在起作用，并忽略任何以前的调整规则系统具有信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f80ff-104">The <xref:System.Globalization.DaylightTime> object returned by the <xref:System.TimeZone.GetDaylightChanges%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method recognizes only the time zone adjustment rule that is currently in effect, and ignores any previous adjustment rules for which the system has information.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f80ff-105">相反，它适用于时它可能还未生效的时间段中时间向后当前的调整规则。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f80ff-105">Instead, it applies the current adjustment rule backward in time to periods when it may not have been in effect.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f80ff-106">若要检索有关特定时区的所有已知的调整规则的信息，请使用<xref:System.TimeZoneInfo.GetAdjustmentRules%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f80ff-106">To retrieve information about all the known adjustment rules for a particular time zone, use the <xref:System.TimeZoneInfo.GetAdjustmentRules%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
